-- BP Investitages Cause of Flaring Incident at Texas City, Texas, Refinery
-- Samantha Zee
-- 2010-08-01T13:58:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-01/bp-investitages-cause-of-flaring-incident-at-texas-city-texas-refinery.html

          
          
             BP Plc  reported intermittent flaring
during a 24 hour period from an undetermined source at its Texas
City, Texas, refinery, according to a  filing  with state
regulators. A site-wide investigation began to determine the
cause, the report said.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
